# Rocq compilation artifacts (P13.5). The proof source
# (`docs/formal/rocq/*.v`) is committed; `coqc` outputs (`*.vo`,
# `*.vos`, `*.vok`, `*.glob`, `.*.aux`) are reproducible from
# source and are produced by the verify.sh advisory gate.
docs/formal/rocq/*.vo
docs/formal/rocq/*.vos
docs/formal/rocq/*.vok
docs/formal/rocq/*.glob
docs/formal/rocq/.*.aux
docs/formal/tla/states/
docs/formal/states/
# TLAPS (`tlapm`) proof cache + fingerprints, and stray TLC/Coq aux files —
# all reproducible from the committed `.tla`/`.v` sources by the verify.sh
# advisory Formal gate (and ad-hoc `tlapm`/`tlc`/`coqc` runs).
docs/formal/**/.tlacache/
docs/formal/**/*.thy
docs/formal/**/.*.aux

.pgmcp.toml
